Hopman Cup tennis results PERTH, Australia, Dec 29  - Results from
the Hopman Cup tennis mixed teams' tournament at the Burswood Dome here
Saturday: Play-off for place in main draw: Italy bt Greece 2-1 Women's
singles: Francesca Schiavone bt Eleni Daniilidou 6-1,6-2 Men's singles:
Davide Sanguinetti bt Vasilas Mazarakis 6-1, 7-6 (8/6) Mixed doubles:
Daniilidou/Mazarakis bt Schiavone/Sanguinetti 4-6, 6-3, 7-6 (10/7)
(Mixed doubles third set decided by super tie-breaker method, with
winner being first to score 10 points). afp01
